"{\"uid\": \"tribune.com.pk-story-2487777-olympic-hero-arshad-nadeem-to-lead-flag-hoisting-at-independence-day-celebrations\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"US  Olympic hero set to lead flag hoisting, says information minister  Federal Minister for Information, Attaullah Tarar, announced that Arshad Nadeem, who recently secured a gold medal at the Paris Olympics, has been invited as the chief guest at Independence Day ceremony on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 2, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8067742750985972, \"rank\": 0.18404547620987086, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadeem will join Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif in the flag-hoisting ceremony, an honour bestowed upon him following his remarkable victory, which has ignited celebrations across the country.\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shehbaz_Sharif\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shehbaz Sharif\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shehbaz_Sharif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shehbaz_Sharif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a press conference, Tarar expressed that \\\"good news is coming from all directions\\\", highlighting the nationwide jubilation over Nadeem's Olympic triumph.\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.9934085430122968, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said that provincial governments, including Punjab, are actively participating in the celebrations.\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 686, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provincial_Assembly_of_the_Punjab\", \"score\": 0.9999147731882099, \"rank\": 8.523407593377375e-05, \"text\": \"Punjab\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provincial_Assembly_of_the_Punjab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provincial_Assembly_of_the_Punjab\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Arshad Nadeem was welcomed in an extraordinary manner; his plane was given a water cannon salute,\\\" Tarar noted.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The minister informed that Nadeem is scheduled to arrive at Islamabad's Nur Khan Airbase at 5pm via a special Pakistan Air Force aircraft and will be escorted with full state protocol.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.37677578518124e-20, \"text\": \"Islamabad\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\"}, {\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Air_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.420355840194968e-24, \"text\": \"Pakistan Air Force\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Air_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Air_Force\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Prime Minister's House has organized a banquet in honour of Arshad Nadeem, whom Tarar described as \\\"a beacon of inspiration for the youth.\\\"\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"score\": 0.5696853631705063, \"rank\": 0.7320552827280842, \"text\": \"House\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\"}, {\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arshad Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added, \\\"Nadeem's journey from Mian Channu to Paris is a unique story that deserves to be captured in a biographical film.\\\"\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mian_Channu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.120606584844088e-15, \"text\": \"Mian Channu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mian_Channu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mian_Channu\"}, {\"begin\": 1236, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999979663698, \"rank\": 2.0336785179769044e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The minister also commended Punjab Chief Minister Maryam Nawaz for personallyvisiting Nadeem's hometo bestow honours upon him, calling it \\\"a commendable gesture.\\\"\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1343, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provincial_Assembly_of_the_Punjab\", \"score\": 0.9999147731882099, \"rank\": 8.523407593377375e-05, \"text\": \"Punjab\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provincial_Assembly_of_the_Punjab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provincial_Assembly_of_the_Punjab\"}, {\"begin\": 1365, \"end\": 1377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryam_Nawaz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maryam Nawaz\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryam_Nawaz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryam_Nawaz\"}, {\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.9934085430122968, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discussing the Independence Day celebrations, Tarar revealed that a major event is planned in Islamabad's F-9 Park, organised under the directives of PM Shehbaz.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.37677578518124e-20, \"text\": \"Islamabad\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamabad\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ministry of Information and Broadcasting will host Pakistan's first drone show, featuring 500 drones.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9877481687673744, \"rank\": 0.012403800502920687, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This event will be non-political, focusing solely on the national flag and promoting patriotism,\\\" he emphasized.\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"New visa policy  The information minister also announced the launch of a new visa policy, simplifying the process for visitors from 126 countries.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He explained, \\\"The visa fee for these countries has been abolished, and the application process has been made significantly easier.\\\"\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He detailed that a simple form with 30 questions will allow applicants to quickly obtain a 90-day visa.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He further stated, \\\"Gulf country residents will also be able to obtain a visa on arrival with just a passport.\\\"\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Regarding tourism, Tarar assured that security for incoming tourists is a top priority, with the Ministry of Interior coordinating closely with provincial governments to ensure the best possible arrangements.\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He highlighted, \\\"The tourism sector, particularly in Gilgit-Baltistan, has seen significant development,\\\" and reiterated the government's commitment to providing quality and affordable accommodation for visitors.\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The minister concluded by expressing his hope that these initiatives would open Pakistan's doors to the world, showcasing the country's natural beauty and cultural heritage.\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2868, \"end\": 2876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9877481687673744, \"rank\": 0.012403800502920687, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Allah has blessed our country with every possible resource, and we want the world to come and see it,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 3075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"COMMENTS  Comments are moderated and generally will be posted if they are on-topic and not abusive.\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3176